msgstr "sudo smbldap-groupmod -x användarnamn gruppnamn"

#: serverguide/C/network-auth.xml:1603(para)
msgid ""
"Additionally, the <application>smbldap-useradd</application> utility can add "
"Samba machine accounts:"
